# alphaTabWebsite (vendor copy)

This directory contains a vendor copy of the alphaTab project's documentation (the "AlphaTeX" docs) pulled from the node_modules/alphaTabWebsite package.

Source: https://github.com/CoderLine/alphaTabWebsite

Files were copied with the script: 

    node scripts/vendor-alphatex.cjs

**License & attribution:** Upstream project license has been copied into this folder as `LICENSE`. Please refer to it for license terms. Original authors and contributors are preserved in the upstream project's repository.
